longBusinessSummary: Scandinavian Enviro Systems AB (publ) develops, builds, owns, and operates facilities for material recovery of resources from used tires in Sweden and internationally. The company's recoverable materials includes carbon black, oil, steel, and gas. Scandinavian Enviro Systems AB (publ) was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Gothenburg, Sweden.
